Package: cortexsec
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3, python3-requests, python3-rich
Description: CortexSec autonomous CLI multi-agent security assessment framework
 CortexSec is a policy-bounded autonomous CLI framework for authorized real-world
 security assessments. It performs non-destructive reconnaissance, attack-surface
 modeling, vulnerability analysis, exploitability reasoning, and report generation
 aligned to OWASP, CVSS, and MITRE mappings.
